{"tid":747643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗欽點神童接班","createTime":"2018-07-18T13:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T14:15:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"713ece860f75d85eef580eba9e7c237237758fc0","tid":747643,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:58:10.000Z","msg":"恭喜皇馬成功爭贏挪威嘅十六歲神童馬田奧迪加特加盟。佢周四正式以皇馬球員身份出席記招，據講轉會費約三百萬歐元，周薪有成十萬歐元。奧迪加特嘅前史卓加斯特隊友仲透露，神童之前同基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）見面，C朗已經指定佢做接班人，話幾年後自己唔可以再好似𠵱家咁入波法，到時就要靠晒佢。"},{"pid":"7f88276655bb388e417fb0e8b8f48947263ad821","tid":747643,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"條友去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4136e6c060056da59aff4d0014bd86fffd579c63","tid":747643,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"新牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a242f3da8d383dccd6ee72270681500d0f1ddc8","tid":747643,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f88276655bb388e417fb0e8b8f48947263ad821","tid":747643,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"條友去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"早幾個月係荷甲傷左"},{"pid":"bdd3003f7f0465d84fac2c714fa1208760af51a7","tid":747643,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"比牙朗燈死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e3ea236ffc5c0986842e7eb974bb0d244f2e06","tid":747643,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"原來神童同麥巴比一樣年紀"},{"pid":"d7af88d2b466c6e3630d7ac7d71f6c2269ff9914","tid":747643,"uid":59246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"仲有巴個個夏利路域呢<img src=\"/assets/fac